  "description": "Sets slider line step and page step delta amount as well as optional step amount of [[CT_SLIDER]] or [[CT_XSLIDER]] with given idc of topmost user [[dialog]]. \n* Click to arrow - move by line\n* Click to scale outside thumb - move by page.\n\n{{Feature|informative|[[CT_XSLIDER]] does not use the ''page'' parameter, it acts as scrollbar when clicked on the bar. It also can only be horizontal.}}",
  "effect_loc": "Unspecified",
